This package collects Thai BDF fonts available in the public.
The license of each font is as per vendors.

* etlthai/*:

  Author:

    Manop Wongsaisuwan <wmanop@netserv.chula.ac.th>

  Copyright:

    These are public domain fonts.

* manop/*:

  Author:

    Manop Wongsaisuwan <wmanop@netserv.chula.ac.th>

  Copyright:

    These are public domain fonts.
    You can find author's statement at the end of manop/README file.

