* poonlap/*:

  Author:

    Poonlap Veerathanabutr <Poonlap.Veerathanbutr@japan.sun.com>

  Copyright:

    Copyright (c) 2001, Poonlap Veerathanabutr.

    License to copy and distribute for both commercial and
    non-commercial use is herby granted, provided this notice
    is preserved.

    Poonlap.Veerathanabutr@japan.sun.com
    This font is my hobby, there is nothing related with Sun Microsystems.
    The motivation is I want to use some Thai font with emacs but I don't
    like the default one. This font is a bit big but the "head" of thai shows
    apparently which I think it is important.

    Produced with bdfedit, a tcl/tk font editing program
    written by Thomas A. Fine  

